net.vivialconnect.model.connector

Class Callback

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.vivialconnect.model.VivialConnectResource
      • net.vivialconnect.model.connector.Callback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Callback
extends VivialConnectResource
    The CALLBACKS resource allows you to set callback URLs for message status, incoming messages, and incoming message fallback. When creating or editing a callback, you must provide a message_type and event_type. e.g. ‘text’ and ‘incoming’
